Ghana’s Commodities Exchange to Start Next Year, Graphic Reports

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-08-22T11:42:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/ghana-s-commodities-exchange-to-start-next-year-graphic-reports.html
Ghana ’s first commodity trading
exchange will be ready by September next year, Daily Graphic
reported.  Ghana ’s Securities and Exchange Commission has carried out
feasibility studies on  the trading platform , while a contractor
is currently drafting the legal framework, the Accra-based
newspaper said, citing Trade and Industry Minister Hannah
Tetteh.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 